column27:
Luxury living at the heart of Burwood

Architecturally designed apartment complex with everything you could wish for - this new home comes with top quality fixtures and fittings, loads of natural light, open plan living areas, neutral toning�s to suit everyone�s pallet, floor to ceiling windows, balconies, storage cage and lift access. 

This apartment is a 2 bedrooms, 2 baths and 1 car space, home to a world-leading university (Deakin University) and elite private schools (PLC, Wesley College), only 14km from Melbourne CBD and close to everything you need around the clock. 

Wake up to the local cafe scene or hit the park for a fitness fix. Take the tram (#75) into Melbourne from right outside your doorstep, 600m to the bus stop or the Monash Freeway in or out of town. Stealing some down time is easy too, with parklands and recreational facilities at every turn.

column117:
Architecturally designed apartment complex with everything you could wish for - this new home comes with top quality fixtures and fittings, loads of natural light, open plan living areas, neutral tonings to suit everyone's pallet, floor to ceiling windows, balconies, storage cage and lift access. 

This apartment is a 2 bedrooms, 2 baths and 1 car space, home to a world-leading university (Deakin University) and elite private schools (PLC, Wesley College), only 14km from Melbourne CBD and close to everything you need around the clock. 

Wake up to the local cafe scene or hit the park for a fitness fix. Take the tram (#75) into Melbourne from right outside your doorstep, 600m to the bus stop or the Monash Freeway in or out of town. Stealing some down time is easy too, with parklands and recreational facilities at every turn.

In light of social distancing, Dynamic Residential will be conducting private, one-on-one inspections of this property by appointment only.
Before booking a time to inspect, please view all photos, the walk-through video and read the description, to ensure the property is suitable for you.

Please get in touch or Book an inspection with us to arrange your private appointment time. 
You can also Apply Online using the link on this page, but please note you will need to have inspected the property prior to being accepted. 
Your health and safety is always important to us, and especially now as we work to stop the spread of COVID-19. We thank you for your cooperation and understanding as we all work together through this time.

column117:
This 2-bedroom apartment is fitted with floor-to-ceiling windows, light timber floors, functional living space and a modern kitchen with high-quality finishes. Also featuring reverse cycle air conditioning, a 6-Star NatHERS and Bosch stainless steel kitchen appliances. 

The building's crystalline facade moves with the changing direction of sunlight and features high-quality amenities within, including BBQ facilities, a dining room, a theatre room, a quiet reading room, a library and an indoor kitchen with bookable facilities.

Close proximity to free city circle tram, Victoria State Library, Carlton Garden, Melbourne Central Station, Emporium, Melbourne Central and QV. 

The photos are taken from a higher level so the views from the window might be slightly different.

INSPECTING IS EASY - Simply scroll down the page to the ‘INSPECTIONS’ subheading and click ‘REQUEST A TIME’ to book a date and time or submit your enquiry. Please ensure you register your details prior to attending the inspection. Once registered, we can keep you updated with available inspection times and any changes or cancellations. So don't miss out, book an inspection today!
To submit an application for this property, simply click the “Get in Touch” button and we will respond with instructions on how to apply.

column27:
Almost Brand New Modern 4 Bedroom Family Home.

Modern 4 bedroom home with master bedroom and ensuite located at the front end of the home with the remaining bedrooms neatly located at the rear, all with built in robes.

Large kitchen/meals area with tiles, plenty of natural light and well placed main bathroom, separate laundry, single lock up garage and maintenance free yard. 

Located in Atherstone Estate Cobblebank's premium location.The property is short distance to the Melton train station, schools and Wood Grove shopping centre. Not far from upcoming Bacchus Marsh Grammar School (opening in 2019) making it an attractive proposition for many.

*Please check open for inspection times prior to each open as times may vary without notice.
